                omnis quia vel quam magnam vitae. Fuga minima, enim numquam
                accusamus voluptas error? Facilis fugiat cum eveniet adipisci
                obcaecati dolore inventore non natus. Excepturi ab eaque
                dolorem, aliquid nulla, neque tempora, facere dicta officia
                asperiores iusto. Officiis debitis perspiciatis deleniti rerum
                praesentium nam facilis ipsam. Ad atque et, iure inventore
                facilis quae sequi dolores. Repudiandae saepe sapiente eum dicta
                tenetur beatae deleniti inventore et, nisi ipsam?
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <Image
          src={botticeli}
          alt="Tableau de Botticelli illustrant le jugement moral"
          title="La calomnie d'Apelle de Botticelli"
          class="w-full aspect-square object-cover mb-3 rounded-xl md:rounded-none"
        />

        <div
          class="bg-tertiary/90 text-white md:hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 rounded-xl md:rounded-none"
        >
          <h3
            class="font-playfair lg:text-3xl text-2xl text-center lg:text-left font-medium pl-5 pt-1 lg:h-[9vh]"
          >
            Intervention en entreprise
          </h3>

          <details class="group">
            <summary
              class="flex cursor-pointer justify-center [&_::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-15 h-15 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:-rotate-180"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
